column6: When message is correct Then sending is success
When message without name Then sending is success
When message without email Then sending is not success
When message without phone Then sending is success
When message without text Then sending is not success
When message has invalid email Then sending is not success
When message has invalid email Then sending is not success
When message has long name Then sending is success
When message has long email Then sending is success
When message has long phone Then sending is success
When message has too long phone Then sending is not success
